games.title: Ancient Dragons Princess
games.description: Enter the magical realm of the Dragon Princess, Rennie, where elegance is paramount. Adorn her in lavish outfits, from velvet gowns to outfits suited for dragon riding. Customize a unique dragon for her, style her hair, add exquisite jewelry, and join Rennie on an extraordinary journey.
games.howToPlayText: Choose outfits for the characters by tapping on them and save the photos to your device!jewelry will also impress you. Go on an adventure with the Dragon Princess!

games.title: Dress Up Anime Girl
games.description: Anime DressUp is a fun online game that lets you style a cute anime princess. With a variety of outfits, hairstyles, and makeup, you can unleash your creativity and fashion skills. Enjoy creating unique looks and make your princess a standout fashionista in her realm!
games.howToPlayText:
Create your perfect anime character!
Make a screenshot and use it as your avatar.

Features:
1. Graphics in anime style
2. 10 692 000 combinations of the appearance
3. Many unusual items
4. Cute cats
5. Screenshot button
6. Random button
